## Phase 1: Basic Widget Setup (15 minutes)

### Step 1: Choose Your Configuration
Visit https://weatherwidget.io/ and customize your widget:

**Key Decisions:**
- Location (city/coordinates)
- Theme selection
- Size preference
- Labels and text
- Temperature unit

